Apache-Session-Ipc version 0.01
===============================

This module provides an other way to store Apache sessions by using shared
memory (UNIX only). It is based on IPC::Shareable.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  - IPC::Shareable
  - Apache::Session of course

